  "prompt": "Can somebody tell me a brand of formal shoes that provide same comfort as that of sport shoes?",
  "response": "One brand of formal shoes known for providing comfort similar to sports shoes is Cole Haiden. Their \"ZER\u00d8GRAND\" line, in particular, combines the elegance of formal footwear with the comfort and flexibility typically found in athletic shoes. The shoes feature materials and technologies such as Grand.OS cushioning, which is designed to offer support and comfort throughout the day.\n\nAnother brand to consider is Ecco. They are well-regarded for their focus on comfort without sacrificing style. Ecco's formal shoes often incorporate features like soft leather uppers, flexible soles, and cushioned insoles that make them feel more like sports shoes.\n\nBoth of these brands have received positive feedback for their ability to provide the comfort of sports shoes while maintaining a formal appearance, making them excellent choices for those who need to wear dress shoes for extended periods.",
